item.description: I already called Pie in the Sky, and they are expecting us. Please dress appropriately as it might be cold and windy. Bring water. I confirmed that the entire path is open. We just need to keep an eye on the weather. Looking forward to meeting everyone.
item.why: Wow! What a great response. We will meet at noon and wait a few minutes for late arrivals. I will send my cell phone # on Saturday to everyone who RSVP'd yes. Since Quicks Hole is closed, we will have lunch at Pie in the Sky.

group.name: South Shore Hike, Bike & Social Club
